metadata.name: Hacker Lab #1
metadata.description: 4,001 Hacker Pads that will grant Holders exclusive access to a wide array of custom hacking tools tailor-made by Experts in the field. Holders will be contacted individually once a Hacker Pad is held for 36 hours. Once contacted, NFT0s will reveal and each holder will commence their own journey into the Hacker Lab.
